                        Our wellness team will reach out to you soon to confirm your appointment and guide you for a rejuvenating experience.\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        <p style=\"font-size:15px; margin: 8px 0 18px 0; color:#009688;\">\n                            <b>Booking ID:</b> <span class=\"highlight\" style=\"background:#fffde7; color:#795548;\">{{doc.name}}</span>\n                            <br>\n                            <b>Service Type:</b> <span class=\"highlight\" style=\"background:#e3fcec; color:#388e3c;\">{{doc.service_type}}</span>\n                        </p>\n                        \n                        <p>\n                            If you have any questions or need to reschedule, please reply to this email or call us at <b>+91-9876543210</b>.\n                        </p>\n                        <a href=\"https://wellnesscenter.example.com/your-booking\" class=\"cta-button\">View Your Booking</a>\n                        <p style=\"margin-top:32px; font-size:15px; color:#388e3c;\">\n                            Thank you for choosing <b>Wellness Center</b>.<br>\n                            We look forward to welcoming you!\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"footer\">\n                        With wellness wishes,<br>\n                        <strong>Wellness Center Team</strong><br>\n                        <em>‚ÄúNourish your body, mind, and soul.‚Äù</em>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</body>\n</html>",
